txt.en: Ereblen can be found at Echad Uial.\n\nYou should bring the remnants of Rauniel to Ereblen.
Remnants of Rauniel can be found in Eithel Gwaur, the Filth-well.\n\nYou should gather the remnants of Rauniel.

'I have heard from Arodor that the remnants of the River Maiden, Rauniel, may still linger within the Filth-well of Eithel Gwaur. If you are to venture inside, seek out the remnants of Rauniel. Arodor hopes that in recovering what remains of Rauniel, we may have a chance to purify the river. It may be a long while before the river ever heals.'
There is much for the White Company to accomplish in reclaiming Minas Ithil from the remnants of Sauron's forces.
'I shall deliver the remains of Rauniel to Arodor. I hope that in our efforts, we shall be able to honour the fallen River Maiden and restore her home to what it once was.'
